      • write

        public List<IndexFileMeta> write(Map<String,DeletionVector> input)
        Write deletion vectors to a new file, the format of this file can be referenced at: PIP-16.
        Parameters:
        input - A map where the key represents which file the DeletionVector belongs to, and the value is the corresponding DeletionVector object.
        Returns:
        A Pair object specifying the name of the written new file and a map where the key represents which file the DeletionVector belongs to and the value is a Pair object specifying the range (start position and size) within the file where the deletion vector data is located.
        Throws:
        UncheckedIOException - If an I/O error occurs while writing to the file.
